{"tid":1778643,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港警察施用暴力、侵害人權展覽","createTime":"2019-12-11T05:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T13:55:13.000Z","uid":235257,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9180da886843bdcff02ee25602b7b5a30f518351","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:53:58.000Z","msg":"【香港警察施用暴力、侵害人權展覽】<br />\n《Exhibition on HK Police Brutality and Human Rights Exploitation 》<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZQKp7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZQKp7f.jpg&h=2445c613&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期 Date：2019年12月14、15日<br />\n時間 Time：1400-2000<br />\n地點 Venue：<br />\n尖沙咀海傍近文化中心 Tsim Sha Tsui Promenade next to Hong Kong Cultural Centre<br />\n<br />\n活動内容 Content：<br />\n向外國遊客及媒體展示香港警察濫用暴力的情況，喚起國際關注<br />\nTo raise public awareness by exhibiting details of HK Police Brutality to foreign tourists and media<br />\n<br />\n聯絡方式contact：hkpbeg@gmail.com"},{"pid":"429819b71e81c57aec03ad654ab3c1a6b5d5e35f","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"國際戰線要大家幫手話俾外國人知"},{"pid":"88dd4a25a4eede0752a825afad93d8669581b6d4","tid":1778643,"uid":146267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ddbf128c5853f4ca6cbad41d79c8055c3be19342","tid":1778643,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff9e5b88de5a279111fedf0a86322d713c1847da","tid":1778643,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:55:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美加議員講對華政策，<br />\n響task2 急要人</span></span><br />\n適逢人權日，世界上人權被打壓嘅國家或地區唔少，當然其中一個亮點係打壓緊香港同新疆嘅中國！<br />\n<br />\n多國政要發推文關注中國打壓人權嘅情況，精選推文遍布task 1 &amp; 2，大家快啲去回應啦！<br />\n<br />\n記得落hashtag #humanrights #HumanRightsDay 呀～<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=6bfb41d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"67ae117a84bfdf4006248eead1ff9ce920e4a9df","tid":1778643,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"520ed392805c8d71a37c4f25edb339c128f14542","tid":1778643,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:10:58.000Z","msg":"到時要show埋張tg map比遊客睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2111563f05e4cf6ab7184ff8999ef7c1e42ddb72","tid":1778643,"uid":4840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:13:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9753630e07accd362e776450d17250801b2d463b","tid":1778643,"uid":43553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"62746b7095bd4f61182bb6f11646b5030ef2a7e8","tid":1778643,"uid":35090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:36:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"69e7745aabd8ca92baeb6612a34ef86e3eec0a43","tid":1778643,"uid":35090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:36:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"665308a050ec9f0607fb279c27183f20858290f6","tid":1778643,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T06:37:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83d4d2670a4ff62e1bbe38d8a292e951255c83ed","tid":1778643,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fbfe42b62b929e3cd4797f777d982a911a3ea3d","tid":1778643,"uid":204835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a123c0d96d1fff8fec72284485ac56f70280bd91","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1e0720af38328006f9c7d329a055e52d2abbe63a","tid":1778643,"uid":36420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"287d22be52eb95eca51be8b5b1f33471728ba0c8","tid":1778643,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c43d2a11bac2a9d6e1eb266f965d83ecff9c05f","tid":1778643,"uid":70370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T10:35:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d04a2b8871aee23d7e694b750a4bd9bf44c5dbac","tid":1778643,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dd6232a9cb92f5c0abf7ffba71aa1d4c13357e1","tid":1778643,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"GOGOGO"},{"pid":"e53925bc7b23e5f2588f468e35d5e3dadd00aa5b","tid":1778643,"uid":76148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:09:18.000Z","msg":"Gj"},{"pid":"1c9fefd08a364988932671d81d6580681b19d587","tid":1778643,"uid":265949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"gogogo"},{"pid":"f1027ad92f717f391967614de5d92e424f63503d","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"熱血時報<br />\n<br />\n【香港警察施用暴力、侵害人權展覽】<br />\n<br />\n在尖沙咀海傍近天星碼頭，有一個名為「香港警察施用暴力、侵害人權展覽」，向外國遊客及媒體展示香港警察濫用暴力的情況，喚起國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RmzLzwc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRmzLzwc.jpg&h=e3e6ff60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D5s5zwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD5s5zwd.jpg&h=3c1c3358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftN5zwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftN5zwd.jpg&h=fa8bf0e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Abg91be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbg91be.jpg&h=85e5d3af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65835f91e556dc3136f78b80ca21f4afe014c4d2","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n【尖沙咀警暴展覽】《 香港警察 施用暴力、侵害人權展覽》繼 10 至 11 月期間舉辦後，今、明兩天下午 2 點 至 8 點，再度於尖沙咀海傍近文化中心巡迴展出。展覽加入了近月的警暴事件，題材內容更為豐富，藉此向大眾、外國遊客及媒體, 展示香港警察使用暴力的情況，以喚起國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n展覽負責人楊小表示香港過去半年的抗爭充滿血汗淚，然而政府沒有聽取民意，卻以中國的執法模式對待香港市民，警察淪為維持政權的左右手。展覽今次設於尖沙咀五星旗杆旁的遊客熱點，期望令更多遊客關注香港的警暴問題和人權狀況，引起國際關注，及揭露香港示威者在極權威脅下的人身安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2700230270062576&amp;id=710476795704610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2700230270062576%26id%3D710476795704610&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=fb686095\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2700230270062576&amp;id=710476795704610</a>"},{"pid":"0de576a5b5c21439ddb6816d8f1326c717e3fa98","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65835f91e556dc3136f78b80ca21f4afe014c4d2","tid":1778643,"uid":235257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"立場新聞<br />\n<br />\n【尖沙咀警暴展覽】《 香港警察 施用暴力、侵害人權展覽》繼 10 至 11 月期間舉辦後，今、明兩天下午 2 點 至 8 點，再度於尖沙咀海傍近文化中心巡迴展出。展覽加入了近月的警暴事件，題材內容更為豐富，藉此向大眾、外國遊客及媒體, 展示香港警察使用暴力的情況，以喚起國際關注。<br />\n<br />\n展覽負責人楊小表示香港過去半年的抗爭充滿血汗淚，然而政府沒有聽取民意，卻以中國的執法模式對待香港市民，警察淪為維持政權的左右手。展覽今次設於尖沙咀五星旗杆旁的遊客熱點，期望令更多遊客關注香港的警暴問題和人權狀況，引起國際關注，及揭露香港示威者在極權威脅下的人身安全問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2700230270062576&amp;id=710476795704610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2700230270062576%26id%3D710476795704610&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwur6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=fb686095\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2700230270062576&amp;id=710476795704610</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T13:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgKjFxG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgKjFxG.jpg&h=edd6dc86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZ9fYjn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZ9fYjn.jpg&h=0f75cf0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fk47Pq3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFk47Pq3.jpg&h=460f3bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A4oTKZp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA4oTKZp.jpg&h=f11fde16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tvbwEq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tvbwEq.jpg&h=46ee6099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HWq64Zr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHWq64Zr.jpg&h=44865fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLOySN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLOySN.jpg&h=402ebe1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POtkpZt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOtkpZt.jpg&h=85de4136&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}